Name:
* Ivan Ukhov RUS disqualified for doping. 




Men's High jump - Athletics - London 2012 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     Athletes competed in a qualifying round followed by the final. Top twelve and ties in the qualifying round and all those reaching the announced qualification limit advanced to the final. Each athlete had three attempts at every height and was eliminated if they had three consecutive failed attempts. The bar was raised until only one athlete was left in the competition. Event facts: Men's High jump competition was held at the Olympic Stadium and 35 athletes participated in the event.
